OL,4,G1130FCome Dine with Me
OL,5,     GAdie, a bar manager, hosts a
OL,6,     Glively night, but tricky
OL,7,     Gcrustaceans challenge guests.
OL,8,G1205FCome Dine with Me
OL,9,     GSir Henry, a vet, relies on charm
OL,10,     Gand wine, as his cooking is
OL,11,     Grather forgettable.
OL,12,G1235FCome Dine with Me
OL,13,     GPippa from Bournemouth serves
OL,14,     Gseafood; will her 'strawberry
OL,15,     Gfish' dessert impress?
OL,16,G1305FCome Dine with Me
OL,17,     GSimone adds flair to the
OL,18,     Gcompetition with a Bajan menu,
OL,19,     Gcreating tension with Pippa.
