OL,4,G1340FCome Dine with Me
OL,5,     GJacqueline aims to impress with
OL,6,     Gher gourmet partridge and black
OL,7,     Gpudding Scotch eggs.
OL,8,G1410FFour in a Bed
OL,9,     GAt The Grange Boutique Hotel in
OL,10,     GCumbria, Jackie and Nigel hope to
OL,11,     Gimpress with high-end suites. But
OL,12,     GSimon finds his room stifling and
OL,13,     Gthe breakfast eggs aren't all
OL,14,     Gthey're cracked up to be.
OL,15,G1440FFour in a Bed
OL,16,     GThe second visit is to Ruth and
OL,17,     GLucy's Rutland Luxury Lodges in
OL,18,     GGreetham. Most of their guests
OL,19,     Gfind luxury in abundance, but
OL,20,     GJackie and Nigel get hot and
OL,21,     Gbothered about the bedding.
