OL,4,G1850FThe Dog House Australia
OL,5,     GLexi hopes to bond with Sam and
OL,6,     GJackson. Bobby and Milly try to
OL,7,     Gmend Johnno's broken heart. And
OL,8,     Gpuppy Cookie may be too much for
OL,9,     Gdancers Ash and Mike.
OL,10,G1955FGrand Designs
OL,11,     GWhile recovering from leukaemia,
OL,12,     GToby planned a radical new home -
OL,13,     Gwrapped around an ancient oak
OL,14,     Gtree - to improve his health and
OL,15,     Gprovide for his family. But
OL,16,     Gbuilding it isn't easy.
OL,17,G2100FGrand Designs
OL,18,     GCan Zahid and Ferzana transform
OL,19,     Gan old coastguard station on an
OL,20,     Gexposed East Yorkshire headland
OL,21,     Ginto a bold, three-storey glass
OL,22,     Gbox of a family home?
